---
description: Enforce typed, linted, well‑documented code.
globs:
  - "**/*.{ts,tsx,py,go,java}"
alwaysApply: false
---

For any file matching the glob:

- Run project linters/formatters (eslint / prettier, ruff / black, etc.).
- All public functions & classes need Google‑style (or PEP 257) docstrings.
- Add meaningful inline comments explaining **why**, not **what**.
- Use strict typing (`mypy --strict`, `tsconfig "strict": true`, etc.).
- New modules must include a README‑style usage snippet at the bottom.
